{"tid":648670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住公屋被偷510萬元首飾","createTime":"2018-05-01T01:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T09:06:37.000Z","uid":50353,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ee07a200b53475bbc35ffbdab59c64a63407cb","tid":648670,"uid":50353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:12:18.000Z","msg":"黃大仙發生懷疑巨額首飾盜竊案。昨晚11時許，39歲女子返回黃大仙下邨龍滿樓單位，其後發現放在手袋內2條頸鏈及1隻手鐲不翼而飛，<span style=\"color: red;\">約值510萬元</span>，於是報警。警方接報到場，懷疑男戶主的10歲女兒與案件有關，帶同女童尋找「失物」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，遇竊女事主以前任職投資銀行，與案中任職髮型師的男戶主相識約17年；今年1月，女事主搬往男方家中居住，但與其女兒不和，兩人經常發生爭吵，案發前雙方再次口角，有人報稱將首飾拋出窗外，其後改口聲稱交給朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180501/s00001/1525135933201?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180501%2Fs00001%2F1525135933201%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=870982f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180501%2Fs00001%2F1525135933201%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=dd736747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180501/s00001/1525135933201?web_push=1</a><br />\n住公屋510萬元首飾"},{"pid":"81c311c5c006d9b298ccd248201acc645f1b57fd","tid":648670,"uid":42925,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"可能買左 你吹得人脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d279b95e2d35498e88f91bb37efd886e70bcafd","tid":648670,"uid":68081,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"81c311c5c006d9b298ccd248201acc645f1b57fd","tid":648670,"uid":42925,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"可能買左 你吹得人脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:22:52.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己up 乜鳩？"},{"